                        Spacious and modern room with a comfortable bed, city view, and premium facilities.
                    </p>

                    <p class="fw-bold text-primary">
                        $1.000.000 / day
                    </p>

                    <a asp-page="/HotelDetails" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
